        <mxCell id="RrWA5nGCw_mJGV-3aDG2-2" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Initial Considerations by statutory auditor&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.&amp;nbsp; Declaration&amp;nbsp; of&amp;nbsp; Indebtedness:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;banks should obtain a declaration of indebtedness before &lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;appointing statutory central/circle/branch auditors&amp;nbsp; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.&amp;nbsp; Internal&amp;nbsp; Assignments&amp;nbsp; in&amp;nbsp; Banks&amp;nbsp; by&amp;nbsp; Statutory&amp;nbsp; Auditors:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt; audit firms should not undertake statutory audit assignment while they &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;are associated with internal assignments in the bank during the same year. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.&amp;nbsp; Planning: &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;as per SA300 undertake&amp;nbsp; the&amp;nbsp; following&amp;nbsp; activities &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;prior&amp;nbsp; to&amp;nbsp; starting&amp;nbsp; an&amp;nbsp; initial&amp;nbsp; audit&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.&amp;nbsp; Communication with Previous Auditor:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;a PCA cannot accept position as auditor without first communicating&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt; with previously held auditor in writing. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.&amp;nbsp; Terms of Audit Engagements:&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;auditor should agree on the terms of the audit engagement with &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;the bank before beginning&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6.&amp;nbsp; Initial Engagements:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;perform procedures as per SA 510&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;7. &amp;nbsp; Assessment of Engagement Risk: &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;assessment of engagement risk is a should be done prior to the acceptance &lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;of anaudit engagement since it affects decision of &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;accepting the engagement and planning&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;8.&amp;nbsp; Understanding the Bank and its Environment:&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;as per SA 315&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
